OL,5,G0010 Emergency Helicopter Medics
OL,6,     FMike's come off his bike and is
OL,7,     Fexperiencing altered sensations in
OL,8,     Fhis legs. Luke's also had a
OL,9,     Fserious bike crash which has left
OL,10,     Fa piece of his bone lying out on
OL,11,     Fthe road.
OL,12,G0100 Ramsay's Hotel Hell
